WHO   — The Droogs — the gang · ultra-violence
WHAT  — The youth-violence at the book's start: loyal, brutal, and quick to betray — two later become the police who beat the conditioned Alex.
WHERE — ACO · A CLOCKWORK ORANGE  Framework inputs: A Clockwork Orange (Anthony Burgess, 1962)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
